{% block content %}
<!-- Monitoring validation string: Want to join in? -->

<section id="splash">
  <h2 class="splash-head"><div class="splash-head-inner"><span class="highlight">We’re a global pack of do-gooders, rabble-rousers and passionate defenders of the Web.</span></div></h2>
  <p class="splash-subhead"><span class="highlight">Want to join in?</span></p>
  <div class="cta-strip">
    <a class="cta ga-career-banner-listings" href="{{ url('careers.listings') }}">View our current openings</a>
    <a class="cta ga-career-banner-internship" href="{{ url('university.index') }}">Apply for an internship</a>
    <a class="cta ga-career-banner-volunteer" href="https://www.mozilla.org/contribute/">Become a volunteer</a>
  </div>
  <div class="splash-credo">
    <div class="contain">
      <h3 class="splash-credo-head">Just call us Mozillians</h3>
      <p>
        We are a proudly non-profit organization driven by a culture of openness and collaboration. It’s a value we hold strong and it’s how we work together, day in and day out.
      </p>

      <div class="splash-video">
        <div class="video-player" data-video-file-name="Are_You_a_Mozillian"
          data-video-ga-interaction="Career Banner Interactions" data-video-ga-name="Are You A Mozillian Video"></div>
      </div>

      <p>
        When you join Mozilla, you’re becoming part of a global community that’s helping to build a brighter future for the Web &mdash; and for everyone.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="teams">
  <h2 class="teams-head">Teams &amp; Roles</h2>
  <div id="teams-intro">
    <div class="teams-intro-contain">
      <p class="teams-blurb">
        Our people are the best and brightest on the planet, and our success comes from when they work collaboratively on projects they care about deeply. Take a closer look at who does what and see where you fit best.
      </p>

      <ul class="teams-nav">
        <li class="teams-hex hex-building">
          <a href="#team-building" class="nosmoothscroll">
            <strong>Building &amp; Designing</strong>
            Working in the open, for the greater good.
          </a>
        </li>
        <li class="teams-hex hex-operations">
          <a href="#team-operations" class="nosmoothscroll">
            <strong>Operations</strong>
            Keep us safe, sound and always running.
          </a>
        </li>
        <li class="teams-hex hex-people">
          <a href="#team-people" class="nosmoothscroll">
            <strong>People</strong>
            Help us find the best. And be one yourself.
          </a>
        </li>
        <li class="teams-hex hex-business">
          <a href="#team-business" class="nosmoothscroll">
            <strong>Business</strong>
            For fast talkers <br>
            and fine printers.
          </a>
        </li>
        <li class="teams-hex hex-marketing">
          <a href="#team-marketing" class="nosmoothscroll">
            <strong>Marketing &amp; Engagement</strong>
            Do cool stuff. <br>
            Tell the world.
          </a>
        </li>
        <li class="teams-hex hex-internships">
          <a href="#team-internships" class="nosmoothscroll">
            <strong>Internships</strong>
            Learn from the best. Impress your folks.
          </a>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <a class="teams-volunteer" href="http://www.mozilla.org/en-US/contribute/">Looking to volunteer?</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <article id="team-building" class="teams-team team-building team-bg">
    <div class="team-contain">
      <h3 class="team-head">Building &amp; Designing</h3>
      <p>
        We are designers, engineers, creators and problem solvers. We work in the fishbowl known as open source, with a clear focus on making the Web better. Working with us, you’ll help build amazing things like Firefox, Rust and more. To be part of the team, we ask that you be awesome, intelligent and proud to be moving the mission forward. Rock on.
      </p>
      <a class="cta" href="{{ url('careers.listings') }}">View Open Positions</a>
    </div>
  </article>

  <article id="team-operations" class="teams-team team-operations">
    <div class="team-contain">
      <h3 class="team-head">Operations</h3>
      <p>
        We are Systems, Security, IT and Finance. Our work at Mozilla is vital to our everyday lives and it keeps you — and everyone in our community — browsing the Web, developing awesome apps and more. We also work hard to keep your identity secure, the lights on and the refrigerators filled. Yep, we do it all.
      </p>
      <a class="cta" href="{{ url('careers.listings') }}">View Open Positions</a>
    </div>
  </article>

  <article id="team-people" class="teams-team team-people">
    <div class="team-contain">
      <h3 class="team-head">People</h3>
      <p>
        People are at the heart of everything that happens here. Our focus is finding the best future Mozillians and helping them join the mission. We provide everyone at Mozilla the tools, resources and support they need to develop, grow and make the world (and the Web, of course) an exceptional place. What do you want to change about the world of work?
      </p>
      <a class="cta" href="{{ url('careers.listings') }}">View Open Positions</a>
    </div>
  </article>

  <article id="team-business" class="teams-team team-business">
    <div class="team-contain">
      <h3 class="team-head">Business</h3>
      <p>
        Business at Mozilla is far from usual. Even for those who wear ties to work, things are a little more unconventional and creative. As the core growth and legal team, our efforts are focused on bringing in new business initiatives and partnerships that will support our current partners, team members, communities and, best of all, mankind. What do you say? Are you ready to get down to business?
      </p>
      <a class="cta" href="{{ url('careers.listings') }}">View Open Positions</a>
    </div>
  </article>

  <article id="team-marketing" class="teams-team team-marketing">
    <div class="team-contain">
      <h3 class="team-head">Marketing &amp; Engagement</h3>
      <p>
        At Mozilla, we have powerful stories to tell — and talented storytellers who share them with the world at large. Working with this team of product marketing, public relations and brand-building dynamos, you’ll have an opportunity to tell thousands of stories from all around the globe, to inspire thousands more and to build our legacy as an innovative, world-changing non-profit. Hope you have your pencils sharpened.
      </p>
      <a class="cta" href="{{ url('careers.listings') }}">View Open Positions</a>
    </div>
  </article>

  <article id="team-internships" class="teams-team team-internships">
    <div class="team-contain">
      <h3 class="team-head">Internships</h3>
      <p>
        Mozilla isn’t just a great place to work. It’s an experience you’ll carry with you throughout your career. As part of our internship program, you’ll have the opportunity to be mentored 1:1 by somebody brilliant, to impact the projects you’ll collaborate on and to never be bored. Ever. From the passionate people you’ll learn from to the chances you’ll have to make the Web a better place, your time with Mozilla will be unlike any other.
      </p>
      <a class="cta" href="{{ url('university.index') }}">Find out more</a>
    </div>
  </article>
</section>

<section id="life">
  <div class="contain">
    <h2 class="life-head">Life at Mozilla</h2>
    <h3 class="life-intro-head">What makes us&#133; us.</h3>
    <p class="life-intro">
      At Mozilla, we like to find the best and most fun ways to do things, and we like to think it shows in all that we do. Throw in a good dose of freedom, teamwork and perks, and you’ve got life at Mozilla. And we haven’t even mentioned the snacks yet.
    </p>
  </div>
  <article id="life-gallery">
    <p class="ally">Gallery of photos showing people brainstorming, working playing, attending conferences, and working together. It also shows the personal touches many Mozillians bring to work: stuffed animals, laptop stickers, a Pac-man ghost made of post-it notes, and FireFox shoe laces.</p>
    <div id="life-gallery-photos">
      <!-- photos loaded here with javascript -->
    </div>
  </article>
  <div class="contain">
    <article id="life-people">
      <h3 class="life-people-head">How we take care of our people</h3>
      <div class="life-people-desc">
        <p>
          We offer a unique, flexible work environment where individual contribution and impact produce results greater than a paycheck and benefits. But pay and benefits are important, so we offer market-competitive salaries and cash-based incentives as well as a full stack of benefits.
        </p>
        <a class="life-people-cta" href="https://assets.mozilla.net/pdf/mozilla-careers-comp-brochure.pdf">Learn more</a>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="community">
  <div class="contain">
    <h3 class="community-head">Community &amp; Culture</h3>
    <div class="community-boxes">
      <div class="community-box community-monument video-player" data-video-file-name="Firefox_Monument_2014"
        data-video-ga-interaction="Community & Culture Interactions" data-video-ga-name="Firefox Monument 2014 Video">
        <h4>Firefox Monument</h4>
        <p>Our tribute to the more than 4,500 people who have helped make Firefox what it is today.</p>
        <p><a href="https://videos.cdn.mozilla.net/uploads/hr/Firefox_Monument_2014.mp4">watch video</a></p>
      </div>
      <div class="community-box community-interns video-player" data-video-file-name="rubic-cube"
        data-video-ga-interaction="Community & Culture Interactions" data-video-ga-name="Creative Interns Video">
        <h4>Creative interns</h4>
        <p>A recent group of interns re-created our beloved Firefox out of Rubik’s Cubes. Showoffs.</p>
        <p><a href="https://videos.cdn.mozilla.net/uploads/hr/rubic-cube.mp4">watch video</a></p>
      </div>
      <div class="community-box community-reps">
        <h4>Mozilla Reps</h4>
        <p>See how we empower volunteer Mozillians in their communities and around the world.</p>
        <p><a href="https://reps.mozilla.org/">visit website</a></p>
      </div>
      <div class="community-box community-desk">
        <h4>Desk companions</h4>
        <p>From the fuzzy to the fierce, they’re always here, silently cheering us on. </p>
      </div>
      <div class="community-box community-festival">
        <h4>Mozilla Festival</h4>
        <p>Our annual gathering of thinkers and inventors from around the world. Consider yourself invited.</p>
        <p><a href="http://mozillafestival.org/">visit website</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

